@@ -0,0 +1,197 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

+  distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,
+  WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.
+  See the License for the specific language governing permissions and
+  limitations under the License.
+--><project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd">
+
+    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
+
+    <name>IdentityConnectors</name>
+    <description>Identity Connectors</description>
+    <groupId>org.syncope.core.identityconnectors</groupId>
+    <artifactId>identityconnectors</artifactId>
+    <version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</version>
+    <packaging>pom</packaging>
+
+    <url>http://syncope.googlecode.com/</url>
+    <prerequisites>
+        <maven>[2.1.0,)</maven>
+    </prerequisites>
+
+    <licenses>
+        <license>
+            <name>The Apache Software License, Version 2.0</name>
+            <url>http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt</url>
+            <distribution>repo</distribution>
+        </license>
+    </licenses>
+
+    <scm>
+        <connection>scm:svn:http://syncope.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/</connection>
+        <developerConnection>scm:svn:https://syncope.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/</developerConnection>
+        <url>http://syncope.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/</url>
+    </scm>
+
+    <issueManagement>
+        <system>Google Code</system>
+        <url>http://code.google.com/p/syncope/issues/</url>
+    </issueManagement>
+
+    <developers>
+        <developer>
+            <name>Francesco Chicchiricc√≤</name>
+            <id>ilgrosso</id>
+            <organization/>
+            <roles>
+                <role>Project Lead</role>
+            </roles>
+            <timezone>+1</timezone>
+        </developer>
+        <developer>
+            <name>Fabio Martelli</name>
+            <id>spallone</id>
+            <organization/>
+            <roles>
+                <role>Project Lead</role>
+            </roles>
+            <timezone>+1</timezone>
+        </developer>
+    </developers>
+
+    <contributors>
+    </contributors>
+
+    <mailingLists>
+        <mailingList>
+            <name>syncope-dev</name>
+            <post>syncope-dev@googlegroups.com</post>
+            <archive>http://groups.google.com/group/syncope-dev</archive>
+        </mailingList>
+        <mailingList>
+            <name>syncope-users</name>
+            <post>syncope-uses@googlegroups.com</post>
+            <archive>http://groups.google.com/group/syncope-users</archive>
+        </mailingList>
+    </mailingLists>
+
+    <properties>
+
+<junit.version>4.8.1</junit.version>
+<groovy-all.version>1.7.2</groovy-all.version>
+        <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>
+<framework.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</framework.version>
+<framework-internal.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</framework-internal.version>
+<test-common.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</test-common.version>
+<test-contract.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</test-contract.version>
+<identityconnectors.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</identityconnectors.version>
+<testbundles.version>0.1-SNAPSHOT</testbundles.version>
+
+    </properties>
+
+    <dependencyManagement>
+
+    </dependencyManagement>
+
+    <repositories>
+    </repositories>
+
+    <build>
+        <defaultGoal>package</defaultGoal>
+        <pluginManagement>
+            <plugins>
+                <plugin>
+                    <inherited>true</inherited>
+                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <configuration>
+                        <source>1.6</source>
+                        <target>1.6</target>
+                    </configuration>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-surefire-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <configuration>
+                        <redirectTestOutputToFile>true</redirectTestOutputToFile>
+                    </configuration>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-checkstyle-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <version>2.5</version>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-jxr-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <version>2.1</version>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-site-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <version>2.1</version>
+                    <configuration>
+                        <locales>en,it</locales>
+                    </configuration>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.codehaus.mojo</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>failsafe-maven-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <version>2.4.3-alpha-1</version>
+                    <executions>
+                        <execution>
+                            <goals>
+                                <goal>integration-test</goal>
+                                <goal>verify</goal>
+                            </goals>
+                        </execution>
+                    </executions>
+                </plugin>
+                <plugin>
+                    <groupId>org.mortbay.jetty</groupId>
+                    <artifactId>maven-jetty-plugin</artifactId>
+                    <version>${jetty.version}</version>
+                </plugin>
+            </plugins>
+        </pluginManagement>
+    </build>
+
+    <reporting>
+        <plugins>
+            <plugin>
+                <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                <artifactId>maven-checkstyle-plugin</artifactId>
+                <version>2.5</version>
+                <configuration>
+                    <configLocation>config/sun_checks.xml</configLocation>
+                    <configLocation>config/maven_checks.xml</configLocation>
+                </configuration>
+            </plugin>
+            <plugin>
+                <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
+                <artifactId>maven-jxr-plugin</artifactId>
+                <configuration>
+                    <aggregate>true</aggregate>
+                </configuration>
+            </plugin>
+        </plugins>
+    </reporting>
+
+    <modules>
+<!--
+    <module>framework</module>
+    <module>framework-internal</module>
+    <module>test-common</module>
+    <module>bundles</module>
+-->
+  </modules>
+
+</project>
